</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="26" pageNumber="734" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="26.[1466,2670,722,1067]" pageId="26" pageNumber="734">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1468,1821,915,948]" pageId="26" pageNumber="734">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Phayre’s Squirrel is widely distributed and its population seemsto be stable. There are no major threats to the population.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
